nuntar (1566) on 27-Feb-09:
White seems to have gone wrong somewhere. 7. Bb3 was better: 7... a5 8. Nxh8 a4 9. Bd5 Nxd5 10. exd5 Nd4 11. c3 and White is okay. ... This move allows me to trade bishop for knight. In so doing, I was originally thinking that once he traded back for the knight that took the bishop I'd be able to snatch the knight it was protecting with my king, but...
...as you can see, that would result in me losing another knight. Instead, being forced to move my knight I see the opportunity to set up a fork of my own.
